{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 ReaMD - Markdown Viewer for REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Dockable markdown viewer designed for audio production workflows. Link text fragments to timeline items, use teleprompter mode for VO, and format text with AI.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Core}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Full markdown rendering (headers, lists, tables, code blocks, blockquotes)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Edit mode - create and modify markdown in REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Dark & Light themes\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Scenario Mode}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Link text fragments to timeline items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Multi-item support with category colors (V/M/F/O)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER group awareness\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Playback position tracking\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Teleprompter}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab VO-focused display with auto-scroll\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Large centered text, progress indicator\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b AI Parse}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Convert unformatted text to markdown using Claude AI\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Customizable prompt template\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Async processing (non-blocking)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Requirements\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER 7.0+\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaImGui 0.10+\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab (Recommended) js_ReaScriptAPI, SWS Extension\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Note\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Tested on macOS Tahoe 26.2. Windows/Linux support expected but not verified.\par}
}

