{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Troubleshooting\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 "ReaImGui not found"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Install ReaImGui via ReaPack: Extensions \u8594 ? ReaPack \u8594 ? Browse packages \u8594 ? Search "ReaImGui"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 AI Parse not working\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Verify your API key is correct in Settings\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Check internet connection\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab On Windows, ensure {\f1 curl} is available (comes with Windows 10+)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Teleprompter not following playback\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Ensure scenario links are set up (fragments linked to timeline items)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Check that linked items exist on the timeline\sa180\par}
